fff","tid":561322,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"9d0ccd25d0387547bbaea74929c04bd56415015c","tid":561322,"uid":20522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T02:37:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T02:46:02.000Z","msg":"🤭🤫"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T06:48:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 秒殺左"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T05:23:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6c46d1792893ec89842c9d2fe8e17322bcb60b9","tid":561322,"uid":67822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1db4f224b254b53565435856c7384f7ab38599ad","tid":561322,"uid":56015,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"a74f0b9e7bcf81afc9ecbed98ba18cf950fce78d","tid":561322,"uid":131245,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"quote":{"pid":"a109fe701da9c44e697f33cd249521e3cef36f49","tid":561322,"uid":56015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T01:42:47.000Z","msg":"2018年02月15日<br />\n<br />\n中美在南海繼續角力。農曆新年前夕，美軍核動力航空母艦卡爾文森號（圖）戰鬥群在南海游弋，美軍網站公佈航母在南海航行的照片，隨行還有兩艘伯克級導彈驅逐艦。英國亦表示下月將有軍艦駛入南海水域，顯示自由航行權。美英此舉明剃北京眼眉。 <br />\n<br />\n英艦下月駛入南海<br />\n美國海軍網站近日上載多張卡爾文森號在南海巡航的照片，包括軍人在艦上的活動、艦載機起飛準備等。網站指，作為美軍例行部署的一部份，卡爾文森號正在西太平洋水域活動，以維護該國際水域「自由航行」。<br />\n該航母戰鬥群是上月離開美國聖地牙哥，前往西太平洋地區部署，同行還有導彈驅逐艦邁耶號（DDG-108）及米高梅菲號（DDG-112）。內地傳媒認為，美軍公開戰鬥群在南海上的行動，警告意味甚濃，可能並非單純在南海到此一遊。<br />\n另外澳洲媒體報道，英國國防大臣韋廉聲言，英國一艘護衞艦下月將從澳洲啟程回英，中途駛入南海，以捍衞航行自由權利。中國外交部發言人洪磊在前天回應稱，中方看到有關報道，指當前南海風平浪靜，有關方面「不要試圖無風起浪」。<br />\n<br />\n[url]<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180215/20306108\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180215%2F20306108&d=f9NUqfofeIko5MxKqjpakIzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=59251e77\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180215%2F20306108&h=cdaf5fd8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180215/20306108</a><br />\n[/url]"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T02:06:54.000Z","msg":"上次遼寧號嚟香港燃油費都用咗唔少，英國老鍊咁遠嚟南海又唔知要用幾錢了。唔知英國啲納稅人點諗呢？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T02:10:38.000Z","msg":"文翠珊: 呢個trip 由上次中國之行R 返嚟嘅錢找數 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T05:32:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}